		<hr size="1"><BR>Greetings.</P><P>I've heard that rangers are one of the best<BR>classes in the game at managing their aggro.<BR>I'd like to hear from some of the more <BR>accomplished and experienced rangers out there<BR>on how you achieve this.  I know there are a <BR>lot of high-level tactics for pulling this off,<BR>but I'd also like to hear about any lower-level<BR>abilities that are useful for this function.</P><P>What tactics do you use to gain aggro, and what<BR>tactics do you use to dump it off?</P><P>Thanks.</P><P>Haloric Wolfsbane<BR>Ranger of the 20th Circle<BR>Prexus Server<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
