		<font size="1" face="Verdana">posted 7/2/2003 11:22:43 PM&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

		
		<a href="MB_editmsg.asp?FID=68&FN=Ranger&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=1988838&TN=Aggro+Management&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=1989011&PL=4">
		<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/edit.gif" border="0" alt="Edit/Delete Message" width="18" height="13"></a>
		
		</font>
		<hr size="1">High level agro management? One word: JOLT! (reduces <BR>Lower level agro management Your best bet would be turn off auto attack and back off the mob until tank takes agro back, or you could root and back off and fight at maximum distance.  At my level to gain agro I ensnare often and use the spell grasping roots and other spells like those to quickly gain agro in a bad situation.  Hope his helps</P><P>Mathezar 58 Outrider<BR>Zumin 35 Mage<BR>&lt;Dawn Breaker&gt;<BR>Prexus<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
